Description: Used Gretsch G6128T Players Edition Jet FT Rosewood - Black PLEASE CONTACT US WITH ANY QUESTIONS OR FOR AN IN-HAND DESCRIPTION What makes this guitar special: Gretsch’s G6128T Players Edition Jet FT is a remarkable solid body electric with excellent playability, high-quality tone, and unmistakable Jet feel. Where this G6128T truly shines is its Players Edition design. This Jet FT has a lower neck set than other Jets, as well as a rolled cutaway and tapered heel, which makes for easy high-fret access. From its killer set of Filter’Trons to its exceptional playability, the G6128T Jet FT will make a fantastic addition to any player’s collection. Cosmetic Condition: Excellent overall condition.
